==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Trifid
<hw>Tri"fid</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L. <ets>trifidus</ets>; tri- (see
<er>Tri-</er>) + the root of <ets>findere</ets> to split: cf. F.
<ets>trifide</ets>.]</ety> <def>Cleft to the middle, or slightly beyond
the middle, into three parts; three-cleft.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

